content.value: My mama always said life was like a box of chocolates. You never know what you're gonna get.
You don't understand! I coulda had class. I coulda been a contender. I could've been somebody, instead of a bum, which is what I am.
Roads? Where we're going we don't need roads.
I'm walking here! I'm walking here!

Google Earth is amazing. They've photographed every road in the world and put them on the computer. You just type it in and you go there. You sit in front of the computer and you think, 'I can go anywhere in the world. Where shall I go?' And we all come to the same conclusion: 'My house.'

Will Brad Pigeon is a 21-year-old student whose life is dominated by solving the murder of his sister, Dai Pigeon. Dai was shot in 2013 and the killer was never brought to justice.
He is a British Christian who defines himself as straight. He is currently at college. He has a severe phobia of cats, and is obsessed with Donald Trump.
Physically, Will is in good shape. He is very tall with olive skin, brown hair and black eyes. He has a tattoo of Donald Trump on his lower back.

caption.en-US: Will Pigeon is a member of our Royal Family

content.value: Phil Matt Wu is a 45-year-old tradesperson who enjoys spreading fake news on Facebook, baking and upcycling. He is loveable and reliable, but can also be very untrustworthy and a bit untidy.
He is an American Christian who defines himself as straight. He has a post-graduate degree in medicine. He is allergic to eggs.

caption.en-US: Phil Matt Wu is a member of our Royal Family

content.value: Tristan James Sweet is a 47-year-old former junior programmer who enjoys stealing candy from babies, meditation and painting. He is loveable and creative, but can also be very disloyal and a bit moody.

He is addicted to alcohol, something which a friend pointed out when he was 16. The problem intensified in 1991. Tristan has lost four jobs as a result of his addiction, specifically: lab assistant, cleaner at a studio, golf caddy and junior programmer.

caption.en-US: Tristan James Sweet is a member of our Royal Family

content.value: Morwenna  Barker is a 54-year-old former theatre actor who enjoys working on cars, jigsaw puzzles and tree shaping. She is creative and creative, but can also be very lazy and a bit impatient.
Morwenna came to Australia from her home country, America, when she was in her early 20s. She started college but never finished the course. She has phobias of apostrophes and buttons

caption.en-US: Morwenna Barker is a member of our Royal Family
